                <p xml:id="KR1h0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:33:47.281+09:00">孟子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:34:38.268+09:00">不要做那本心所不願做的事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:36:09.916+09:00">不要想那本心所不願想的私欲，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:41:08.51+09:00">做人的道理像這樣就是了。　[“不為，不欲” 就義理上言之　(bu wei and bu yu must be taken in a pregnant sense CH)]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T19:53:11.646+09:00"/>
                </p>
